Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Campus Alpha is a three-level building with an onsite cafe suitable for a range of occupiers in the medical and professional services sector. The building enjoys a strategic position within the Robina Health Hub – sitting adjacent to QLD Health, Primary Health Care Medical Centre, Robina Hospital, Robina Private Hospital and a range of medical consulting specialists throughout CBDRobina.  Existing major occupiers include ClearSmiles, QLD Health – Dental Clinic, Horizon Housing and Shine Lawyers.

The building has a central Gold Coast location with easy access to the Pacific Motorway, a major four-lane highway feeding to Brisbane and into northern NSW.

- Suites from 72sqm up to whole floor of 2,200sqm
- Whole floor is easily subdividable to accommodate a range of occupiers – this space is fully fitted and furnished
- 72sqm has new fitout in place – ideal for a range of medical consulting specialists
- Onsite visitor parking
- Onsite café
- Signage opportunities

For further information or to arrange an inspection, contact the exclusive leasing agent via the links above.

Acuity Business Park – Building 2 now leasing

Building 1- now complete and fully leased.
Building 3- fully pre committed.

Building 2- 1,850sqm total is now available across ground and level 1. The floors can be split to a tenants needs. The basement is already complete and estimated construction will be complete by December 2021. Integrated fitouts can be negotiated. 

Located in the heart of Robina’s growing corporate community, Acuity Business Park will be one of the Gold Coast’s premier commercial office developments.

Within walking distance to the Robina Town Centre and train station, this intelligently designed business park is surrounded by world class dining, shopping, health and education.


Key Features;

* PCA A Grade design with minimum 4 star NABERS Energy

* Secure basement car parking (280 bays) and ample visitor car 
  parking 
* High impact signage opportunities
* End of trip facilities including bike racks, lockers and showers
* Onsite café sought
* Contemporary light-filled break out areas.
